218
00:19:57,460 --> 00:19:58,420
Eine Katastrophe!

219
00:19:58,560 --> 00:19:59,320
Die beiden Kinder!

220
00:19:59,660 --> 00:20:00,420
Die Zwillinge!

221
00:20:00,500 --> 00:20:01,500
